sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant A as FastAPI
  participant M as ML Inference
  participant R as RAG Agent
  participant D as MongoDB/Cosmos
  U->>A: POST request
  A->>A: Pydantic validation + logging
  alt Prediction
    A->>M: feature payload
    M-->>A: model output
  else Agent Q&A
    A->>R: question
    R-->>A: answer + context
  end
  A->>D: save request/response log
  A-->>U: JSON response
